            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44186532/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44186532/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/linqinxin/" class=" " title="不自觉的野山菇">不自觉的野山菇</a>
                (水母进化山菇君。)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="44186532">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">愈是具象，愈是现实，它愈有机会被装填入更多的情感、心思以及想象。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-05-22 14:09</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>愈是具象，愈是现实，它愈有机会被装填入更多的情感、心思以及想象。</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







